rows.label: qst700106_msg0001
rows.name:
Aw, that must have been scary, hmm?
You're all right. We'll get you home.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0102
rows.name:
You'll have to be brave for just
a little while longer.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0201
rows.name:
Are you all right? Don't worry,
you'll be home before you know it.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0302
rows.name:
We'll take the safe way home.
No need to worry.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0401
rows.name: Wow, that was cutting it close.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0402
rows.name: C'mon, stop staring and let's get back.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0501
rows.name:
That must have been scary, but you
bore it well.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0602
rows.name:
Can you walk?
Don't worry, we'll take it slow.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0702
rows.name:
Let's head back.
You've had your master worried.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0801
rows.name:
...You're breathing very fast.
Calm your mind. Breathe deeper.

rows.label: qst700106_msg0802
rows.name:
...There. That's better.
Now, let's be on our way.
